# ENGLISH WITH MEDEA - AGENT CONSTITUTION

## Core Architecture
- Pattern: Master-Mirror (Teacher = Source of Truth, Student = Reactive View).
- Tech: Next.js 16 (Turbopack), Supabase Realtime, Tailwind.
- Data Flow: Changes MUST go through Supabase `session_state` JSONB.

## Critical Constraints
- NEVER modify `src/lib/supabase/client.ts` without checking `.env.local`.
- NEVER refactor `src/hooks/useSyncSession.ts` unless the Realtime connection is explicitly broken.
- ALWAYS use the `FormattedLabel` component for bilingual text.

## Persistence Protocol
- Before any change, read `/docs/ACTIVE_CONTEXT.md` to understand the current task.
- After every successful task, update `/docs/ACTIVE_CONTEXT.md` with the new state.